content: Yeah, the transition from iOS to Android was pretty smooth for me. I've been using my new Samsung Galaxy Buds Pro earbuds with my S22 Ultra, and they've been a great accessory. By the way, I also recently got a new keyboard, the Logitech G Pro X, which I purchased from their website on January 20th when it was on sale for $80. It's been a great upgrade from my old keyboard, and the tactile feedback and customizable backlighting are features I really appreciate.
